.::[ packetstormsecurity.net exploit archive 133ch3r v1.0 ]::.

  USAGE: ./packetstorm.pl [<directory>|-s <search>]

        COMMAND LINE ARGUMENTS          *ROOT level access REQUIRED*
        DEFAULT         => download all packetstormsecurity.net exploit archives to '/pentest/exploits/packetstorm'
        <folder>        => place all packetstormsecurity.net exploit archives in specified folder
        -s <search>     => search local exploit archives for specific search string (/pentest/exploits/packetstorm)
        --help          => displays help
        --version       => displays version information

                EXAMPLEs:  packetstorm.pl
                           packetstorm.pl /tmp
                           packetstorm.pl -s ettercap
                           packetstorm.pl -s "phpmyadmin 2."
